summary: As a student who studies at Erasmus University, I always want to have a chance for practising my skills. I already finished a part of the courses in International Business Administration. In university, I always do teamwork with students who come from different countries, these unique experiences not only help me perform better as a role in the team but also helps me improve the ability of diversity thinking. After I graduated from high school, I worked for an educational institution as a teaching assistant, keeping relationships with students and teachers is always the key. In the meanwhile, the experience of buying and selling stock in the Chinese stock market since 2016 not only helps me understand commercial banking but also inspire me to explore more in this area.
